text: Vilhelm Lindgrén (3 July 1895 - 26 July 1960) was a Finnish swimmer. He competed in two events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1895 births Category:1960 deaths Category:Finnish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Finland Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tampere
